data.message: Deploy hybrid path discovery v2 system: Successfully deployed. V2 endpoint live on Render. Pre-seeded cache paths (Music→Africa, Coffee→Mathematics) return in 0ms. Non-cached paths return in ~70ms (vs 15.5s before). System gracefully handles failures with helpful hints.
